Rawalpindi, Aug 2 (APP): ISPR has released a new Song on Youm-e-Istehsal, highlighting Kashmir uprising, sufferings of Kashmiris & human rights violations by Indian Army.
The song coincides with August 5th, marking one year of abrogation of Article 370 and lockdown & curfew in Indian Illegaly Occupied Jammu and Kashmir (IIOJK).
